---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — vinReliability"
  description="Privacy policy for vinReliability LLC products including vinQuality, vinFMEA, and vinReliability."
  keywords="vinReliability privacy policy, data privacy, vinQuality privacy"
  canonical="/privacy"
>
  <Header />

  <main>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white py-16 sm:py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <div class="reveal">
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
            Privacy Policy
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-500">Last updated: March 2026</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Policy Content -->
    <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="reveal prose prose-slate max-w-none">

          <p class="text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            vinReliability LLC ("we," "us," or "our") operates the vinQuality, vinFMEA, and vinReliability software products and the vinqms.com website. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our products and services.
          </p>

          <!-- Information We Collect -->
          <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Information We Collect</h2>

          <h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800">Account Information</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            When you create an account or request a demo, we collect your name, email address, company name, and job title. This information is used to provision your account and provide customer support.
          </p>

          <h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800">Usage Data</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            We collect anonymized usage data including pages visited, features used, session duration, and general interaction patterns. This data helps us improve our products and identify areas where users may need additional support.
          </p>

          <h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800">Cookies and Tracking</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            We use essential cookies to maintain your session and preferences. We may also use analytics cookies to understand how visitors interact with our website. You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings.
          </p>

          <!-- How We Use Information -->
          <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">How We Use Information</h2>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-base text-slate-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>Service Delivery:</strong> To provide, maintain, and improve our software products and customer support.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>Product Improvement:</strong> To analyze usage patterns and develop new features that better serve our users.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>Communication:</strong> To send account notifications, security alerts, product updates, and respond to support requests.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> To comply with applicable laws, regulations, and legal processes.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <!-- Data Sharing -->
          <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Data Sharing</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties. We may share data only in the following circumstances:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-base text-slate-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>Service Providers:</strong> With trusted third-party providers who assist in operating our services (hosting, payment processing, email delivery), under strict data protection agreements.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law, regulation, or legal process, or to protect the rights and safety of our users and company.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets, with appropriate notice to affected users.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <!-- Data Security -->
          <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Data Security</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data, including encryption in transit (TLS) and at rest, access controls with role-based permissions, regular security audits, and secure infrastructure hosted on reputable cloud providers. While no system is completely secure, we are committed to protecting your information using commercially reasonable safeguards.
          </p>

          <!-- Your Rights -->
          <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            You have the following rights regarding your personal information:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-base text-slate-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>Correction:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete personal data.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your personal data, subject to legal retention requirements.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>Export:</strong> Request an export of your data in a portable format.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>Opt-Out:</strong> Unsubscribe from marketing communications at any time.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@vinreliability.net" class="text-[#0D9488] hover:text-[#0F766E] transition-colors font-medium">support@vinreliability.net</a>.
          </p>

          <!-- Cookies -->
          <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Cookies</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our website and applications use two types of cookies:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-base text-slate-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for authentication, session management, and core functionality. These cannot be disabled without impacting your ability to use the service.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#0D9488]"></span>
              <span><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> Used to collect anonymized usage statistics to help us improve our products. These can be disabled through your browser settings or cookie preferences.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <!-- Changes to Policy -->
          <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or applicable laws. We will notify you of material changes by posting the updated policy on our website and, where appropriate, by sending an email notification. The "Last updated" date at the top of this policy indicates when it was last revised.
          </p>

          <!-- Contact -->
          <h2 class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your data, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6">
            <p class="text-base text-slate-700 font-semibold">vinReliability LLC</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
              Email: <a href="mailto:support@vinreliability.net" class="text-[#0D9488] hover:text-[#0F766E] transition-colors">support@vinreliability.net</a>
            </p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
              Website: <a href="https://vinqms.com" class="text-[#0D9488] hover:text-[#0F766E] transition-colors">vinqms.com</a>
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
